<section>
  <h3 class="dummy-h3">Component API</h3>
  <p class="dummy-paragraph">Here is the API for the component:</p>

  <dl class="dummy-component-props">
    <dt>type <code>enum</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Has a border and a background color. Names
        <code class="dummy-code">global</code>
        and
        <code class="dummy-code">page or inline</code>
        are temporary and subject to change.</p>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li class="default">global</li>
        <li>page or inline</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt>isCompact <code>boolean</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>
        <code class="dummy-code">isCompact</code>
        is a variation on the
        <code class="dummy-code">page or inline</code>
        alert type ONLY. An
        <code class="dummy-code">isCompact</code>
        alert does NOT have a border. An
        <code class="dummy-code">isCompact</code>
        alert does NOT have a background color.
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>true</li>
        <li class="default">false</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt>intent <code>enum</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p><code class="dummy-code">intent</code>
        result in a default
        <code class="dummy-code">icon</code>, which can be overriden.
        <code class="dummy-code">intent</code>
        chooses a background color, border,
        <code class="dummy-code">titleText</code>
        color (if applicable), and
        <code class="dummy-code">bodyText</code>
        color (if applicable).
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li class="default">neutral</li>
        <li>highlight</li>
        <li>success</li>
        <li>warning</li>
        <li>critical</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt>hasIcon <code>boolean</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li class="default">true</li>
        <li>false</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">icon <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>Use this parameter to show an icon. Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">hasIcon=true</code>.
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable value:</p>
      <p>Any
        <a href="https://flight-hashicorp.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Flight icon</a>
        name.
      </p>
    </dd>

    <dt>titleText <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>
        The title text in the alert.
        <code class="dummy-code">titleText</code>
        OR
        <code class="dummy-code">bodyText</code>
        is required.
      </p>
    </dd>

    <dt>bodyText <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>The body text in the alert.
        <code class="dummy-code">titleText</code>
        OR
        <code class="dummy-code">bodyText</code>
        is required.</p>
    </dd>

    <dt>hasButton <code>boolean</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>true</li>
        <li class="default">false</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">buttonIcon <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>Use this parameter to show an icon on the Button. Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">hasButton=true</code>.
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable value:</p>
      <p>Any
        <a href="https://flight-hashicorp.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Flight icon</a>
        name.
      </p>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">buttonText <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>Use this parameter to show text on the Button. Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">hasButton=true</code>.
      </p>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">buttonIconPosition <code>enum</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>
        Positions the icon before or after the text. Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">hasButton=true</code>
        and if
        <code class="dummy-code">buttonText</code>
        exists.
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li class="default">
          leading
        </li>
        <li>
          trailing
        </li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt>hasLinkStandalone <code>boolean</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>true</li>
        <li class="default">false</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">linkStandaloneIcon <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>Use this parameter to show an icon on the Link (Standalone). Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">hasLinkStandalone=true</code>.
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable value:</p>
      <p>Any
        <a href="https://flight-hashicorp.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Flight icon</a>
        name.
      </p>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">linkStandaloneText <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>Use this parameter to show text on the Link (Standalone). Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">hasLinkStandalone=true</code>.
      </p>
    </dd>

    <dt class="dummy-indent">linkStandaloneIconPosition <code>enum</code></dt>
    <dd class="dummy-indent">
      <p>
        Positions the icon before or after the text. Exists if
        <code class="dummy-code">haslinkStandalone=true</code>
        and if
        <code class="dummy-code">linkStandaloneText</code>
        exists.
      </p>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li class="default">
          leading
        </li>
        <li>
          trailing
        </li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt>hasDismiss <code>boolean</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Acceptable values:</p>
      <ol>
        <li class="default">true</li>
        <li>false</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>

    <dt>“splattributes”</dt>
    <dd>
      <p><code>...attributes</code> spreading is supported on this component.</p>
    </dd>
  </dl>
</section>